article.headline: UC Irvine 73, UC Davis 59
article.story: IRVINE, Calif. (AP) -- Patrick Sanders scored 15 points and Michael Hunter added 13 to lead UC Irvine to a 73-59 victory over UC Davis Thursday. Mark Kelley scored eight of his 12 points in the game's first five minutes for the Anteaters (13-16). Dominic Calegari led Davis (4-21) with 21 points and seven rebounds. He scored his team's first 11 points over a 7-minute, 44-second span, then scored seven in a row in the second half. Thomas Juillerat scored 11 points and C.J. Portz had 10 for the Aggies, who lost nine in a row.
